race.comment: GEORDIE LAD (7) boasts a strong record this course with two wins and three minors from five tries. Placed last time (22.68) at this track in a Grade 5/6, finishing third and beaten 4 lengths. Makes strong appeal on best. BERN WEST BOLTER (5) scored two back in quick then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 5.5 lengths 4th at this track (22.77). Was a winner at her only start from this draw. Key player if finds best. IMPRESS ROCKS (6) had been racing well prior to his last start fifth at this track following a Mix 5 win three back with a third placing. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. CITY OF LOVE (2) took charge early and was never headed last time out. Right in the mix again.
